synonyms.synonym: SubName: Phosphoinositide-3-kinase, catalytic, gamma polypeptide, isoform CRA_a

protein.specific_function: 3-phosphorylates the cellular phosphoinositide PtdIns- 4,5-biphosphate (PtdIns(4,5)P2) to produce PtdIns-3, 4,5- triiphosphate (PtdIns(3,4,5)P3). Links G-protein coupled receptor activation to the secondary messenger PtdIns(3,4,5)P3 production

go_class.description: phosphotransferase activity, alcohol group as acceptor
